---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import Card from "../components/ui/Card.astro";
---
<PageLayout title="Stack">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Capabilities</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-white/70">Grouped by how I ship and maintain systems.</p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <Card class="p-5">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white/50">Backend</div>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-white/75 space-y-2">
                <li>Go services, APIs, signed URLs, storage abstractions</li>
                <li>Postgres modeling, migrations, performance profiling</li>
                <li>Auth + permissions with least-privilege design</li>
            </ul>
        </Card>

        <Card class="p-5">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white/50">Security / Privacy</div>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-white/75 space-y-2">
                <li>Threat modeling mindset: reduce attack surface</li>
                <li>Safe defaults, auditability, secure-by-design UX</li>
                <li>Local-first and encryption-friendly architecture</li>
            </ul>
        </Card>

        <Card class="p-5">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white/50">Frontend</div>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-white/75 space-y-2">
                <li>Astro + TS + Tailwind, accessible components</li>
                <li>State machines for complex UI flows</li>
                <li>Performance budgets + clean navigation</li>
            </ul>
        </Card>

        <Card class="p-5">
            <div class="font-mono text-xs text-white/50">Infra / DX</div>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-white/75 space-y-2">
                <li>Self-host friendly deployment patterns</li>
                <li>Observability basics: logs/metrics/traces</li>
                <li>Repo hygiene: conventions, automation, docs</li>
            </ul>
        </Card>
    </div>
</PageLayout>
